{
  "enabled": false,
  "version": "1",
  "name": "validate-steering-architecture",
  "description": "Validate the KIRO-RULES.md architecture and scenario documents",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Please validate the KIRO-RULES.md architecture:\n\n**Instructions**:\n1. Use context-gatherer subagent to read KIRO-RULES.md and check completeness\n2. Use context-gatherer subagent to verify 6 scenario documents exist in .kiro/powers/gemini-fullstack/steering/\n3. Use context-gatherer subagent to verify 5 core documents exist in .kiro/docs/\n4. Analyze the summaries to check cross-references between documents\n5. Validate document structure and formatting from the gathered context\n\n**Follow KIRO-RULES.md**: Never directly use readFile, readMultipleFiles, or listDirectory. Always use context-gatherer subagent for reading and analyzing project documentation.\n\nProvide a detailed report of any issues found."
  }
}
